\id JUD
\h Yudu
\mt1 TIRE
\mt1 TE YUDU U YORUA
\ip Yudu u sɑ̃ɑwɑ Yesu Kirisin wɔnɔ turo. Yesuɡibu kpurowɑ u tire te yoruɑ. Sɑɑ ye, ɡɑbɑ seewɑ ben suunu sɔɔ bɑ sɔ̃ɔsi weesuɡinu sɔ̃ɔsimɔ ni nu koo de ben Yesun yiɡbɛnu nu kɑrɑnɑ. Tɔn be bɑ sɔ̃ɔsi ni mɔ̀ mi, bɑ wɑ̃ɑwɑ kom bɛrɛtɛkɛ sɔɔ. Adɑmɑ Gusunɔ u koo bu kɑm koosiɑ nɡe mɛ u yeruku tɔmbu ɡɑbu kuɑ be bɑ ǹ nùn mɛm nɔɔwɛ. N weenɛwɑ Yesuɡibu bu kɑ tii yinɑ. Domi bɑ Gusunɔn ɡɑri mɔ yi yi sɑ̃ɑ ɡem sere kɑ bɑɑdommɑɔ. Yiyɑ n weenɛ bɑ n dɑ dendi.
\is1 Tire ten kpunɑɑ
\iq1 1. Tɔbiribu, nɑɑsu 1-2.
\iq1 2. Keu koosio weesuɡibu, nɑɑsu 3-16.
\iq1 3. Yiirebu kɑ kirɔ, nɑɑsu 17-23.
\iq1 4. Siɑrɑ dɑ̃ɑkibu, nɑɑsu 24-25.
\c 1
\s1 Tɔbiribu
\p 
\v 1 Nɛ Yudu, Yesu Kirisin yoo, nɛ wi nɑ sɑ̃ɑ Yɑkɔbun wɔnɔ, nɑ bɛɛ tire teni yoruɑmmɛ, bɛɛ be Gusunɔ Bɑɑbɑ u sokɑ. U bɛɛ kĩ, mɑ u bɛɛ kɔ̃su Yesu Kirisin sɔ̃.
\p 
\v 2 Gusunɔ u n bɛɛ wɔnwɔndu kɑ ɑlɑfiɑ kɑ kĩru sosiɑmmɛ.
\s1 Keu koosio weesuɡibu
\r (I mɑɑ mɛɛrio Piɛɛ II, 2:1-17)
\p 
\v 3 Nɛn kĩnɑsibu, nɑ rɑɑ kĩ n bɛɛ tireru yoruɑ, nɛ kɑ bɛɛn fɑɑbɑn ɡɑrin sɔ̃, ɑdɑmɑ wee tɛ̃ n kuɑ tilɑsi n kɑ bɛɛ tire teni yoruɑ n kɑ bɛɛ hɑniɑ koosiɑ kpɑ i kɑ ɡɑri yi i nɑɑnɛ doke sunɑ yi Gusunɔ u wiɡibu wɛ̃ nɔn teeru sere kɑ bɑɑdommɑɔ.
\v 4 Domi tɔn kɔ̃sobu ɡɑbɑ duɑ ɡbɛnum bɛɛn suunu sɔɔ be bɑ Gusunɔn durom ɡɔsikiɑ, bu kɑ ben kom kɔ̃sum ɡɑfɑrɑ wɑ, mɑ bɑ Yesu Kirisi yinɑ, wi u sɑ̃ɑ bɛsɛn Yinni boko. Sɑɑ ɡɑsɔ ɡɑsɔn diyɑ bɑ yoruɑ ye n koo bu deemɑ siribun biru.
\p 
\v 5 Bɑɑ mɛ i ye kpuro yɛ̃ sɑ̃ɑ sɑ̃ɑ, kɑ mɛ, nɑ kĩ n bɛɛ yɑɑyɑsiɑ mɑ ye Yinni Gusunɔ u Isirelin tɔmbu wɔrɑ sɑɑ Eɡibitin tem di u kpɑ, yen biru u be bɑ ǹ nɑɑnɛ doke kɑm koosiɑ.
\v 6 I mɑɑ wɔllun ɡɔrɑdobɑ yɑɑyo bèn ɑyerɑ kun bu turie, mɑ bɑ ben tiin wɑ̃ɑ yeru ɡɛmɑ bɑ deri. Gusunɔ u kɑ bu yɔni bɔkuɑ, u kpɛ̃ɛ yɑm wɔ̃kuru sɔɔ bɑ kɑ siribun tɔ̃ɔ bentembereru mɑrɑ.
\v 7 Mɛyɑ mɑɑ Sodomu kɑ Gomɔrɑ, kɑ wuu si su su sikerenɛ, si kpuron tɔmbu bɑ mɑɑ dɑɑ bɛrɛtɛkɛ kuɑ, tɔn durɔbu kɑ tɔn durɔbu bɑ tii sɑnkunɑmɔ. Bɑ wuu si kpeerɑsiɑ kɑ dɔ̃ɔ wi u ku rɑ ɡbi, mɑ n kuɑ yĩreru tɔmbun sɔ̃.
\p 
\v 8 Kɑ mɛ, tɔn kɔ̃so be mɑɑ, ben bwisikunu sɔɔ bɑ kɑ torɑnu tii disi dokemɔ, bɑ ǹ wiruɡibu wiru kpĩiyɑmmɛ mɑ bɑ wɔllun yiikoɡibu wɔmmɔ.
\v 9 Adɑmɑ Misɛli, wi u sɑ̃ɑ Gusunɔn ɡɔrɑdobɑn wiruɡii, u ǹ kɑ̃kɑ u Setɑm tɑɑrɛ wɛ̃ kɑ wɔmburu dɔmɑ te bɑ sɑnnɑ bɑ Mɔwisin ɡoru sikirinɛ, ɑdɑmɑ u Setɑm sɔ̃ɔwɑwɑ u nɛɛ, “Yinni Gusunɔwɑ u koo nun ɡerusi.”
\v 10 Adɑmɑ tɔn kɔ̃so be, ye yɑ kun bu yeeri yeyɑ bɑ wɔmmɔ, ye bɑ mɑɑ mɔ̀ kɑ mɑrumɑruru nɡe yɛɛ yeyɑ yɑ bu kɑm koosiɑmɔ.
\v 11 Nɔni swɑ̃ɑruɡibɑ bɑ sɑ̃ɑ. Domi bɑ Kɑɛnin yirɑ swĩi, bɑ tii sure torɑru sɔɔ bu kɑ ɑre wɑn sɔ̃ nɡe mɛ Bɑlɑmu u kuɑ, mɑ bɑ Gusunɔ seesi nɡe mɛ Kore u kuɑ, mɑ bɑ tii kɑm koosiɑ.
\v 12 Tɔn be, bɑ sɑ̃ɑwɑ sɑnkɑrɑ kowobu bɛɛn tɔ̃ɔ bɑkɑ ni i rɑ ko kĩrun sɔ̃ sɔɔ, bɑ kɑ bɛɛ dimɔ, kɑ sekuru sɑriru, bɑ ben tii nɔɔrimɔ tɔnɑ. Bɑ sɑ̃ɑwɑ nɡe ɡuru winu ni woo ɡɑ bɔrikiɑmɔ, ni nu ku rɑ kɑ ɡurɑ nɛ. Bɑ sɑ̃ɑ nɡe dɑ̃ɑ ni nu dɛrurɑ nu ǹ binu mɔ, ni bɑ wukɑ kɑ ɡbiniɔ, ni nu ɡu mɑm mɑm.
\v 13 Bɑ sɑ̃ɑwɑ nɡe nim wɔ̃kun nim kure ni nu kukumɔ. Nɡe mɛ nu nin yɑkeru kɔ̃ɔmɔ mɛyɑ bɑ mɑɑ ben sekuru sɑri kom sɔ̃ɔsimɔ. Bɑ sɑ̃ɑwɑ nɡe wɔllun kperi yi yi yin swɑɑ bie, Gusunɔ u bu yɑm wɔ̃ku te tɑ kpɑ̃ yiiye tè sɔɔ bɑ koo du kɑ bɑɑdommɑ.
\p 
\v 14 Enɔku mɑɑ, wi u sɑ̃ɑ Adɑmun sikɑdobun tɔ̃kɑ nɔɔbɑ yiruse u Gusunɔn ɡɑri ɡeruɑ ben sɔ̃ u nɛɛ, wee, Yinni u sisi kɑ win ɡɔrɑdo dɛɛro dɑbi dɑbiru
\v 15 u kɑ bɑɑwure kpuro siri kpɑ u kɑ Gusunɔn bɛɛrɛ yɛ̃ru sɑriruɡibu kpuro tɑɑrɛ wɛ̃ ben kom kɔ̃sum kpuron sɔ̃ mɛ bɑ kuɑ Gusunɔn ɡɛndun sɔ̃, kɑ mɑɑ ɡɑri kɔ̃sin sɔ̃ yi torobu be bɑ ǹ Gusunɔn bɛɛrɛ yɛ̃ bɑ nùn ɡerusi.
\v 16 Tɔn be, bɑ rɑ n wure, ɡɑ̃ɑnu sɑri ni nu rɑ bu wɛ̃re, ben binɛ bu kpɑre. Bɑ rɑ woo kɑnɑ ɡɑri ɡere, bɑ mɑɑ tɔmbu ɡɑri dori sɔ̃ɔmɔ bu kɑ yɛ̃robun ɡɑ̃ɑnu wɑ.
\s1 Yiirebu kɑ kirɔ
\p 
\v 17 Adɑmɑ bɛɛ nɛn kĩnɑsibu, n weenɛ i ɡɑri yi yɑɑyɑ yi bɛsɛn Yinni Yesu Kirisin ɡɔrobɑ rɑɑ ɡeruɑ.
\v 18 Domi bɑ bɛɛ sɔ̃ɔwɑ mɑ sɑnɑm dɑ̃ɑkim sɔɔ tɔn yɑɑko kowobɑ koo nɑ be Gusunɔn bɛɛrɛ yɛ̃ɛ sɑrirɑ koo de ben binɛ yɑ n bu kpɑre.
\v 19 Beyɑ bɑ kɑ kɑrɑnɑɑ nɑɑmɔ, bɑ ben tiin bwisikunu mɔ̀, bɑ ǹ Hunde Dɛɛro mɔ.
\v 20 Adɑmɑ bɛɛ nɛn kĩnɑsibu, i tii tɑ̃sisio bɛɛn nɑɑnɛ doke dɛɛrɑbu sɔɔ i n kɑnɑru mɔ̀ kɑ Hunde Dɛɛron dɑm.
\v 21 I tii nɛnuɔ Gusunɔn kĩru sɔɔ, i n kɑ bɛsɛn Yinni Yesu Kirisin wɔnwɔndu mɑrɑ te tɑ koo kɑ bɛɛ wɑ̃ɑru te tɑ ku rɑ kpe nɑɑwɑ.
\p 
\v 22 I ben wɔnwɔndu wɑɑwo be bɑ ɡɔ̃rusu yiru yiru mɔ̀.
\v 23 I n ɡɑbu ɡɑwɑmɔ dɔ̃ɔ sɔɔn di i n bu fɑɑbɑ mɔ̀. I mɑɑ ɡɑbun wɔnwɔndu wɑɑwo tɑ n kɑ bɛrum mɛnnɛ, ɑdɑmɑ i n ben torɑnu tusɑ sere kɑ ben yɑbenɔ ni ben dɑɑ yɑ disinu tɛɛni.
\s1 Siɑrɑ dɑ̃ɑkibu
\p 
\v 24-25 Gusunɔ turo sɑ̃ɑ bɛsɛn Fɑɑbɑ kowo wi u koo kpĩ u bɛɛ kɔ̃su i ku kɑ wɔrumɑ, kpɑ u bɛɛ terɑsiɑ win yiiko sɔɔ tɑɑrɛ sɑriru sɔɔ kɑ nuku dobu. Wiyɑ u yiiko kɑ kpɑ̃ɑru kɑ dɑm kɑ ɡirimɑ mɔ sɑɑ bɛsɛn Yinni Yesu Kirisin min di, yee yellun di, kɑ tɛ̃, sere kɑ bɑɑdommɑɔ. Ami.
